    "ensures that the customized instruction is applied.",
    "Simple Chat also lets researchers specify that the assistant should initiate the conversation.",
    "If the assistant_first attribute is set to True, the LLM initiates the conversation as soon as the chat window opens.",
    "This is especially useful in studies where the LLM is expected to guide participants proactively from the start.",
    "For studies involving multimodal interaction, Simple Chat supports vision-language models."
